# 🚀 Featured Projects

## 🔹 SafeGuard — AI Insurance Claims Agent

AI-powered insurance support platform using voice agents and real-time analytics.

### ⚙️ Tech Stack

`TypeScript` `Fastify` `Supabase` `PostgreSQL` `ElevenLabs` `Twilio` `React`

### ✨ Features

* AI voice workflows for automated claims support
* Real-time dashboard infrastructure
* Claim analytics and tracking
* Callback scheduling and escalations
* Scalable PostgreSQL schema architecture

---

## 🔹 ZeroLayer — Agentic File Storage CLI

Trustless decentralized storage infrastructure for autonomous AI agents.

### ⚙️ Tech Stack

`JavaScript` `IPFS` `Filecoin` `Web3` `CLI`

### ✨ Features

* Decentralized file storage
* Autonomous payment workflows
* Agent-based verification systems
* CLI tooling for AI-native infrastructure

---

## 🔹 Skyfall — Weather Risk Analytics Platform

Real-time weather analytics and DeFi mutual aid platform.

### ⚙️ Tech Stack

`Next.js` `TypeScript` `REST APIs`

### ✨ Features

* Live meteorological analytics
* Interactive dashboards
* Real-time weather feeds
* Community-based risk-sharing system

